{"tid":952094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無肛三胞胎】停工湊B驚心臟病發 貧農父母：醫藥費係3倍","createTime":"2018-12-22T21:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T17:55:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6955ab0db72a6386f1f4e65347814fde398a4036","tid":952094,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T21:22:06.000Z","msg":"新生命的誕生，本來會令一家人帶來喜悅。可是，貴州這個來自農村的家庭，生了三胞胎男嬰，可是他們一出生就沒有肛門，並患有心臟病、腎積水等併發症，所需的醫療費用，也乘以三倍，沉重的經濟負擔，讓這一家人愁雲密佈。<br />\n三胞胎現時已11個月大，被病魔折磨得骨瘦如柴。他們的父母潘賢斌和雷美玲來自農村，家中已有一名長子，他們想再生個二胎寶寶給哥哥作伴，誰知懷了三胞胎。內地記者本年3月曾經探訪潘賢斌家，當時三胞胎的外婆和母親雷美玲正忙着餵奶、更換造口袋。因為三胞胎天生沒有肛門，只能靠造口袋排泄，一天要更換五、六次。三胞胎還有心臟先天性發育不良的問題，隨時會因心臟病發送院，嚴重的話可能送命。<br />\n當時，潘賢斌指出，三胞胎要進行肛門再造手術，手術共分為3期，每次分隔3個月，今年3月現已完成第一次造瘺手術，在前腹開一個造口排出大便；護理3個月後，進行造肛手術；第三次手術就要遷腸回肛。全部手術費需要30萬元人民幣（約34萬港元）左右。<br />\n可是，潘家家境清貧，根本無法應付沉重的經濟負擔，「我們一家人都在照顧這3個孩子，沒時間出去打零工，也根本沒有收入來源，孩子常換用的造口袋護理排便太貴，為省錢，我們只有在淘寶閒魚網購別人用剩下，奶粉也不敢買貴的，娃娃還是瘦得很！」雷美玲說着，淚水就在眼眶內打轉。<br />\n「每次看到這3個可愛的新生兒面孔，作為一名父親我不會放棄。」父親潘賢斌哽咽地說，他將3名兒子改名為「潘才廣、潘才財、潘才源」，就是希望他們未來不會因為錢的事情煩惱。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Jow699.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Jow699.png&h=eda9f84d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYFb699.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYFb699.png&h=f91b6110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QtbOpWQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQtbOpWQ.png&h=1045c5fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181223/59055240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181223%2F59055240&d=LH01F22bqoHxxGzYtuV5gMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b8e9b647\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181223%2F59055240&h=5e199bfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181223/59055240</a>"},{"pid":"e467736f3d2800497bd73aa66a158e898b6d0f3a","tid":952094,"uid":100136,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T21:29:50.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要支那農村<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc335eaf83c6f07df3876b890206cce4af6c755","tid":952094,"uid":2772,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T21:34:31.000Z","msg":"慌唔係俾人連鬧三次生仔冇屎忽"},{"pid":"ffa0fd2fb875b7e952d95dd5a27cacd0475ffed0","tid":952094,"uid":136662,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0bc335eaf83c6f07df3876b890206cce4af6c755","tid":952094,"uid":2772,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T21:34:31.000Z","msg":"慌唔係俾人連鬧三次生仔冇屎忽"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T21:52:35.000Z","msg":"陰質野做太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d644a35ae0c0589f3f3b707d5cb767ccaa0a1ab3","tid":952094,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T00:52:29.000Z","msg":"生仔冇屎忽<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AhrKJTC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAhrKJTC.gif&h=8806e9f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要三個<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6ecb9a07201b0f248c36fa7cca729d193caf9e","tid":952094,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T01:00:34.000Z","msg":"呢d叫唔好彩<br />\n三胞胎有幾大機會中先"},{"pid":"78a4e47ab9bfe87a606c81364644a73fb6acca64","tid":952094,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T01:00:59.000Z","msg":"原來生仔屎忽呢句咒語真係work<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce94a8c8369166736770ff6032fcdd022290ce3","tid":952094,"uid":280,"like":0,"disl